    "Additionally, for students who lack sufficient knowledge about each topic, this exercise may be too advanced.",
    "High-dosage tutoring, where students work closely and frequently with tutors, has been shown to improve outcomes (Kraft et al., 2021).",
    "Research shows that tutoring that focuses student attention, allows students time to ask and answer questions, and actively work on problems can help students learn (Chi & Roy, 2008).",
